				<li><strong>Early Warning System:</strong> Alert when customers show churn signals</li>
				<li><strong>Intervention Triggers:</strong> Launch save campaigns before they leave</li>
				<li><strong>Win-Back Sequences:</strong> Reactivate churned customers</li>
			</ul>

